transaction.explanation: This X12 Transaction Set contains the format and establishes the data contents of the Purchase Order Transaction Set 850 for use within the context of an Electronic Data Interchange EDI environment. This transaction set should not be used to convey purchase order changes or purchase order acknowledgment information.
